text: @FedExHelp - I ordered a backpack with one day shipping from @amazon for my vacation tomorrow and it was supposed to arrive tonight... I just checked taking and it has arrived in the state... What can I do it get it by morning?

@leiagracea Leia, my apologies to you for the delay in your delivery.  Please contact our customer service team and ask if you can pick up the package before it's loaded into the van for delivery. The station does not open until 9 AM. 
Rochelle
